What is the area, in square units, of triangle $ABC$? [asy]
unitsize(1.5mm);
defaultpen(linewidth(.7pt)+fontsize(8pt));
dotfactor=4;

pair A=(-3,1), B=(7,1), C=(5,-3);
pair[] dots={A,B,C};
